Kipi-plugins 0.5.0 - Release date: 24/07/2009
------------------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES:

PrintWizard  : Added support for 2-1/3" x 3-1/3" pictures.
DNGConverter : Update internal XMP sdk from Adobe to version 4.4.
PrintImages  : Added multiple pages printing.
PrintWizard  : Page layout into template.xml file, custom templates can be added now.

